                     <interp inst="t18310217-157-off946" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310217-157-cd947" type="crimeDate">22nd of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-157-off946 t18310217-157-cd947"></join>, 5 lbs. of nails, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310217-157-victim1566" type="victimName">
                           William Philip 
                           Dammerham
                        <interp inst="t18310217-157-victim1566" type="surname" value="Dammerham"></interp>
