                     <interp inst="t18310217-157-person1570" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . These are my nails; here is my own mark on the paper.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-157-person1571">
                  GEORGE 
                  TIMOTHY KIRTLAND
               <interp inst="t18310217-157-person1571" type="surname" value="TIMOTHY KIRTLAND"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-157-person1571" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-157-person1571" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the beadle of St. Ann, Westminster. On Thursday, the 19th of May, in the sixth year of the late King, the prisoner was convicted for stealing two umbrellas and one coat, and was ordered to be transported for seven years - I attended the trial, and know he is the man.</p>
